[[File:Tuckeys lane.jpg|thumb| Tuckey's Lane]]
[[File:Tuckey's Lane.JPG|thumb|right|Tuckey's Lane]]
'''Tuckey's Lane''' is a lane of the old town of Gibraltar. It connects [[Line Wall Road]] to [[Main Street, Gibraltar|Main Street]]. The Italian Consulate and the Maharaja Indian Restaurant are located here as is [[Barclays Bank]] and [[Sacarello's]] restaurant on the corner with Main Street.<ref name="CollectifAuzias2012">{{cite book|author1=Collectif|last2=Auzias|first2=Dominique|last3=Labourdette|first3=Jean-Paul|title=Andalousie 2012-2013|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ljMOmIAp9eYC&pg=PA264|date=16 February 2012|publisher=Petit Futé|language=French|isbn=2-7469-5730-2|page=264}}</ref>

